# Input

```svelte
{#await promise}
<p>Loading...</p>
{:then value}
<p>The value is {value}</p>
{/await}

```


# Formatted

```svelte
{#await promise}
	<p>Loading...</p>
{:then value}
	<p>The value is {value}</p>
{/await}

```
